@page "/characters/{Slug}"
@layout PublicLayout

<PageTitle>Characters · comicplus</PageTitle>
<SectionContent SectionName="page-title">Characters</SectionContent>

<div id="kyshumu" class="character-profile">
    <div class="character-header">
        <h2>Kyshumu</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flexbox character-content">
        <div class="character-art">
            <img src="https://pre00.deviantart.net/bdec/th/pre/i/2017/358/e/c/kyshumu_blaise_by_sheldon227-dbxpy7r.png" alt="Kyshumu Blaise" />
        </div>
        <div class="character-description">
            <p>
                Kyshumu Blaise is the Chief of the ReNet Network and number 1 ranked Cybervator. He is impulsive
                and mistrustful but loyal and protective towards those he cares about. Although he is a Chief he
                still tries to fight every chance he gets so that he can retain his number one ranking.
            </p>
            <p>
                When Kyshumu fights —while going into burst drive mode—he pounces into action and roars with a
                glass shattering battle cry thanks to his lion-leopard he synergizes with.
            </p>
            <p>
                He originally started with just a leopard Cyber.Beast but was given a lion cyberbeast by his wife
                Tomasina as a courting gift. He now uses a Lion-Leopard hybrid combined with his fire element and
                strength ability. This enables him to have an unorthodox fighting style — although his specialty
                is strength, he combines it with his fire element to generate power in short bursts. This gives
                him incredible jumping ability, allowing him to be as fast as most speed-type cybervators and
                jump as high as many flying types can fly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

@code {
    [Parameter] public string? Slug { get; set; }
}
